description: Charming Apartment on the upper west side of Manhattan! Located between Broadway and Central Park. Blocks from the Natural History Museum and Central Park Reservoir/Great Lawn. Close to 3 major subway lines and cross town bus. Located in the heart of the Upper West Side, in a pre-war building - located less than 1 block away from Central Park. Cafes, museums and shops are literally right on the corner when you step outside. I will provide you with keys to the outside front door and apartment during your stay. Sheets, blankets, comforters, towels, and pillows are available. A blow dryer is available too. If you forget any amenities, there is a 24 hour Duane Reade and CVS (drug store/pharmacy/general store) around the corner. I will be available via email. My friend will be nearby if anything comes up. I will also leave the supers number just in case. gem of NYC - Central Park- Less than 1 block away! Entrances are located at 81st street and 85th street (Strawberry Fields).  Riverside Pa
name: Charming 1-bedroom - UWS Manhattan
